    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >你是机器中的一条沙丁鱼，但生活有这么简单吗？这个地方迫使你与同类做出一项预言性的选择。你是会帮助同类，还是将它们引入歧途？它们也会反过来这样对待你吗？<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1854430/extras/1327cf4e1c45727cbdcacc34f734b895.poster.avif?t=1738335580\" width=600 height=250 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1854430/extras/1327cf4e1c45727cbdcacc34f734b895.webm?t=1738335580\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1854430/extras/1327cf4e1c45727cbdcacc34f734b895.mp4?t=1738335580\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >鱼会疼吗？</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >鱼是怎样炼成的是一段叙事驱动的短小体验，玩家可以与鱼对话并做出各种选择。体验身为沙丁鱼的终极权力幻想、从同类比目鱼那里寻求指引、在广阔海洋中深思鱼生意义吧。扭动、翻滚，命运就掌握在鱼鳍褶子里。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1854430/extras/041534c7dfade629d2408e1aa3047da9.poster.avif?t=1738335580\" width=600 height=250 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1854430/extras/041534c7dfade629d2408e1aa3047da9.webm?t=1738335580\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1854430/extras/041534c7dfade629d2408e1aa3047da9.mp4?t=1738335580\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >鼓鳍你的勇气</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >探索一个潮湿污秽、充满罪恶和沙丁鱼的世界。居民住在芳香四溢的神秘之地，从大厅里回荡的呼呼声、砰砰声和轻轻的拍打声中寻求慰藉。尽管少有鱼能够直面所有鱼都必须做出的可怕抉择：向上还是向下？但你不是懦夫，对吗？</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1854430/extras/5dbd629c07a9d8a1eb09ee81e04a598d.poster.avif?t=1738335580\" width=600 height=250 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1854430/extras/5dbd629c07a9d8a1eb09ee81e04a598d.webm?t=1738335580\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1854430/extras/5dbd629c07a9d8a1eb09ee81e04a598d.mp4?t=1738335580\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >一部音乐史诗</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >人人都需要从存在的恐怖中得到喘息。特别收录Tri-Tachyon的原创歌曲《Little Lily Swing》</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1854430/extras/e6bd6c0755164a96ae3e03d0131f3679.poster.avif?t=1738335580\" width=600 height=250 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1854430/extras/e6bd6c0755164a96ae3e03d0131f3679.webm?t=1738335580\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1854430/extras/e6bd6c0755164a96ae3e03d0131f3679.mp4?t=1738335580\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >翻烦了？滚滚看！</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >收录了精彩的类《块魂》免费DLC——《The Last One and Then Another》。在变成庞然大物的崇高任务中，吸收肉块和同类鱼吧。由《缄默祸运》的船长科里特别出演！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >感受一些东西！</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >这些沙丁鱼看起来很真实，所以你真的可以相信它们拥有情感。我保证！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >警告！游戏含有：</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >-诱发密集恐惧症的画面。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >-可能会让人不安的话题。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >-一小撮精液。</p>",
